u1ee3ng, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn to\u00e0n c\u1ea7u.<\/span><\/li>\r\n \t<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">H\u01a1n 2.100 ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf b\u1eb1ng ti\u1ebfng Anh.<\/span><\/li>\r\n \t<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i h\u1ecdc b\u1ed5ng \u0111a d\u1ea1ng t\u1eeb ch\u00ednh ph\u1ee7 v\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc.<\/span><\/li>\r\n \t<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Chi ph\u00ed h\u1ee3p l\u00fd so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c qu\u1ed1c gia T\u00e2y \u00c2u kh\u00e1c.<\/span><\/li>\r\n \t<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">M\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111a v\u0103n h\u00f3a, th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n v\u1edbi sinh vi\u00ean qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf.<\/span><\/li>\r\n \t<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">V\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung t\u00e2m ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng di chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c n\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00e2n c\u1eadn.<\/span><\/li>\r\n \t<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i vi\u1ec7c l\u00e0m v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u01b0 cao sau khi t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p.<\/span><\/li>\r\n<\/ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-79707\" src=\"https:\/\/thedeweyschools.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/10\/kinh-nghiem-du-hoc-ha-lan-7.png\" alt=\"Sinh vi\u00ean qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 Lan trong m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdc nh\u00f3m\" width=\"800\" height=\"500\" \/>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sinh vi\u00ean qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 Lan trong m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdc nh\u00f3m<\/span><\/i><\/p>\r\n<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><em><strong>&gt;&gt;XEM TH\u00caM:<\/strong><\/em><\/span>\r\n<ul>\r\n \t<li><em><strong><a href